Hi Dario,

The problem is that the devel version of BSgenome that is currently
online (1.21.0, which is what you have) is out-of-sync with some
recent changes in Biostrings/IRanges.

You need BSgenome >= 1.21.3, which is the latest version in svn.
Unfortunately, because of some build issues, this version didn't
make it to the public repo yet. In the meantime, you can always grab
it from svn by following the instructions here:

   http://bioconductor.org/developers/source-control/

Let us know if you need help with this.

Cheers,
H.


